#==========================================================
# EVENT BOOKING FLOW
#==========================================================

### 1. Calculate Event Booking (Preview — no transaction created)
# Use this to show the user a price breakdown before they commit.
# Replace ticketId with the _id of the ticket sub-document in Event.tickets[]
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}",
  "qty": 2,
  "discountCode": ""
}

### 2. Calculate Event Booking WITH Promo Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}",
  "qty": 1,
  "discountCode": "SUMMER2026"
}

### 3. Initiate Event Booking (Creates PENDING transaction)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}",
  "qty": 2,
  "discountCode": ""
}

### 4. Confirm Payment (Mock — transitions PENDING → PAID)
# Use the transactionId returned from the initiate step
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "{{transactionId}}"
}

### 5. Get My Event Tickets (Upcoming)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/list?bookingType=EVENT&type=upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 6. Get My Event Tickets (Past)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/list?bookingType=EVENT&type=past
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 7. Get All My Event Tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/list?bookingType=EVENT
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 8. Get Ticket Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/detail/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 9. Generate Share & Download URLs
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/public/generate-urls/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 10. Get Public Ticket Detail (No auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/public/detail/{{transactionId}}

#==========================================================
# EVENT ATTENDEE MANAGEMENT (Organizer)
#==========================================================

### 11. Get Event Attendees List
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 12. Get Event Attendees — Checked-in Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees?status=checked-in
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 13. Get Event Attendees — Not Checked-in
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees?status=not-checked-in
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 14. Get Event Attendee Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 15. Scan QR Code (Gate Keeper Check-in)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/scan-qr
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrCodeData": "TICKET-REPLACE_TXN_ID-REPLACE_USER_ID-1234567890"
}

### 16. Cancel My Event Booking (User cancellation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "{{transactionId}}",
  "reason": "Cannot attend due to personal reasons"
}

#==========================================================
# RECENT BOOKINGS (Organizer Dashboard)
#==========================================================

### 17. Get Recent Event Bookings (Organizer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/recent?bookingType=EVENT&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 18. Get Recent Event Bookings — Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/recent?bookingType=EVENT&status=PAID&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 19. Get Recent Event Bookings — Filter by Event
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/recent?eventId={{eventId}}&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
